## Constraints

- Dashboard widgets lazy-loaded (Suspense + RSC)
- Reports aggregation: PostgreSQL aggregate queries (materialized view post-MVP if slow)
- Charts: recharts (no D3 complexity — MVP)
- Keyboard shortcuts: `?` help modal, `G+T` tasks, `G+D` dashboard, `Esc` close modal
- Accessibility full audit: axe-core PR gate + manual screen reader test
- Bundle budget strict — charts lazy-loaded only on report pages

## Done Definition

- [ ] Dashboard: 4 widget + permission-gated visibility
- [ ] Dashboard data queries: stale time 60s, refetch on window focus
- [ ] Reports: process count by type + status, completion time median/p95, user activity timeline
- [ ] Report date range picker + CSV export
- [ ] Keyboard shortcut help modal (`?`)
- [ ] Accessibility: all routes pass axe-core with zero violations
- [ ] Manual screen reader test: dashboard + tasks + process detail
- [ ] Loading states: skeleton shapes match final layout (no layout shift)
- [ ] Empty states: first-run guide + filter-empty distinction
- [ ] `pnpm lighthouse` — all critical routes score 80+ performance, 90+ a11y

## Explicit Don'ts

- Custom chart library (recharts yeter)
- Drag-and-drop dashboard (fixed layout MVP)
- Multi-dashboard support (single dashboard MVP)
- Advanced analytics (funnels, cohorts — post-MVP)
- Dashboard widget builder (admin UI) — post-MVP
- Real-time dashboard (poll yeter)

## Related ADRs

- ADR-0028: recharts over D3 for MVP
- ADR-0029: Aggregate queries vs materialized views (defer)

